WEBVTT

00:00:59.672 --> 00:01:00.860
His memory.

00:01:00.884 --> 00:01:04.616
(Clip) Reporter: We saw you on television
and you remembered a ton of plays.

00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:06.832
AG: Sean McVay can recall, on command,

00:01:06.856 --> 00:01:09.763
almost any moment
he's ever seen on a football field.

00:01:10.460 --> 00:01:13.165
Listen to him being grilled
by a couple sports reporters

00:01:13.189 --> 00:01:15.965
about completely random plays
from past seasons.

00:01:15.989 --> 00:01:18.953
(Clip) Reporter 1: Week 12,
Saints at Rams,

00:01:18.977 --> 00:01:21.331
4-29 in the second quarter,

00:01:21.355 --> 00:01:23.834
second-and-seven, on the Saints' seven.

00:01:24.775 --> 00:01:25.925
What happened?

00:01:26.609 --> 00:01:28.514
Sean McVay: Oh, Josh Reynolds' touchdown

00:01:28.538 --> 00:01:30.655
off-scheduled play
versus a three-man rush.